Court has plea colloquy with Mr. James.  
Defendant enters GUILTY plea to Count 2.  
Court finds plea to be entered knowingly, voluntarily and intelligently and finds the deft guilty.  
Cts 1, 3 and 4 are dismissed and read-in.  
3:36 pm  Argument by Atty Johnson as to sentence.  
3:46 pm  Argument by Atty Anderson as to sentence.  
