1)  Twelve (12) months in the Walworth County Jail with work release privileges to commence on or before September 30, 2016.  Court STAYS Six (6) months of this conditional jail time.  Jail may be served in Jefferson County under electronic monitoring if available to him;  

2)  No contact with M.T.K. without Agent's consent;  
3)  No alcohol.  No drugs or drug paraphernalia;  
4)  No weapons;  
5)  Submit DNA sample and pay surcharge;  
6)  Pay court costs and DOC supervision fees;  
7)  AODA assessment and follow through with recommendations;  
